{"tid":1856241,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我係瑪嘉烈醫院護士，多謝大家支持醫護罷工","createTime":"2020-02-01T13:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T17:23:06.000Z","uid":41701,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"a1a266b23bbbfa2b59a1a61bcdcec085380bbdda","tid":1856241,"uid":41701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:47:01.000Z","msg":"請大家大力支持我地嘅罷工活動，多謝<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n香港專職醫療人員及護士協會<br />\n《第一次特別會員大會》<br />\n<br />\n本會將舉辦第一次特別會員大會，<br />\n就有關罷工事宜作出表決。<br />\n<br />\n日期：二月二日（星期日）<br />\n時間：1900-2300<br />\n地點：兆基創意書院（聯合道135號）<br />\n<br />\n💡只限已繳交會費的合資格會員（可出示電子會員證或payme 截圖證明。）<br />\n<br />\n💡現場會設有會員即場收費時段。<br />\n<br />\n💡即場收費時段：2/2/20 1830至大會完結。<br />\n<br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n政府幾時先肯聆聽民意？<br />\n全面封關，為時未晚<br />\n<br />\n加入工會<br />\n集結力量<br />\n<br />\n如希望加入我們工會，可填寫以下google form，我們會盡快回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/J3s4mkS3MxjkRpsC7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJ3s4mkS3MxjkRpsC7&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=30724349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/J3s4mkS3MxjkRpsC7</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港專職醫療人員及護士協會<br />\n<br />\n#工會 #特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n#罷工<br />\n<br />\n#武漢肺炎 #新型冠狀病毒"},{"pid":"70dc90279d8b199162fb3976207cf5bf6c8d7dd3","tid":1856241,"uid":301067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"76ecdb1fe330cd6a9a3b690d5ec3a3976ca09e7b","tid":1856241,"uid":41701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"30a646d8edb57764e6626dbc86c91947ba0a49e7","tid":1856241,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor