"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:20:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebfec9df93105f8654d9ba3de74f446101897b2a","tid":1856241,"uid":343712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"我唔同你講政治，純粹講常識。<br />\n如果你係一個消防員，係3級大火現場，眼見好快會升到5級大火。你手頭上嘅裝備都係殘缺不全，唔足以應付5級大火，而氧氣筒得翻兩分鐘唔夠。然後你call增援要求裝備，而管理層同你講明白你嘅憂慮，希望你憑意志用念力衝入去救火，因為人終於有一死。<br />\n<br />\n咁你如果咁都照衝入去嘅，唔係叫堅守崗位，而係叫無知。"},{"pid":"194157f654eaa921533d6ef180154924fba5dcd5","tid":1856241,"uid":324041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:24:15.000Z","msg":"睇到果d乜乜主席總監咁賤格淨係識講風涼話，相信好多香港市民係會支持妳哋嘅!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b49da811d337033a21eb32f25e63c5e2991189","tid":1856241,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}